title: Winning numbers drawn in 'Pick 10' game
maintext:
ALBANY, N.Y. (AP) _ The winning numbers in Saturday evening’s drawing of the New York Lottery’s “Pick 10” game were:
03-06-07-10-14-20-26-33-38-39-40-43-44-46-56-68-71-73-76-78
(three, six, seven, ten, fourteen, twenty, twenty-six, thirty-three, thirty-eight, thirty-nine, forty, forty-three, forty-four, forty-six, fifty-six, sixty-eight, seventy-one, seventy-three, seventy-six, seventy-eight)
